 for the Beetle, the Golf hatchback, and the ID series of electric vehicles."], "scores": [0.6409636399203328, 0.5229260904067731, 0.5135055858757028, 0.4642951739912779, 0.4523443018921001], "model_name": "harrier", "document_ids": ["Tesla", "Rivian", "Lucid", "Ford", "Volkswagen"]}}